cs.DC, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a service for distributed training of deep neural networks, which involves topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). The focus on scalability and efficiency also suggests cs.DC as the most likely category.
